text.tspan: This is me, the fat guy, with my lovely family. I have
two other daughters from their birth mom, Laura. We
adopted Whitney, the bride in the middle, when she
was three days old. This is her wedding to Carter
We are eternally grateful for the wonderful husbands
that our daughters have chosen. Tyra, is on the far
right, and my wife Kim is next to her.
